---
import Container from "../ui/Container.astro";

const challenges = [

{
icon:"💸",
title:"Operating Costs Keep Increasing",
description:"Reduce repetitive manual work and improve operational efficiency using intelligent automation."
},

{
icon:"⏳",
title:"Employees Spend Too Much Time on Manual Tasks",
description:"Free your team from repetitive work so they can focus on higher-value activities."
},

{
icon:"📞",
title:"Customers Expect Faster Responses",
description:"Deliver 24/7 customer support using AI assistants and intelligent chatbots."
},

{
icon:"📊",
title:"Business Decisions Take Too Long",
description:"Gain real-time insights with AI-powered dashboards and predictive analytics."
},

{
icon:"📄",
title:"Too Much Paperwork",
description:"Automate document processing, approvals and reporting."
},

{
icon:"🚀",
title:"Unsure Where AI Fits",
description:"Our AI Discovery Workshop identifies quick wins with measurable ROI."
}

];
---

<section class="section-padding bg-white">

<Container>

<div class="text-center">

<span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-red-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-red-700">

Business Challenges

</span>

<h2 class="mt-6 text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">

Do These Challenges Sound Familiar?

</h2>

<p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl text-slate-600">

Most Singapore SMEs face similar operational challenges.
The good news is that many can be solved quickly using practical AI.

</p>

</div>

<div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

{

challenges.map((item)=>(

<div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition">

<div class="text-5xl">

{item.icon}

</div>

<h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

{item.title}

</h3>

<p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">

{item.description}

</p>

</div>

))

}

</div>

<div class="mt-16 rounded-3xl bg-blue-50 p-10 text-center">

<h3 class="text-3xl font-black">

If You Answered "Yes" to Any of These...

</h3>

<p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600">

Let's identify where AI can create the biggest impact for your business.

</p>

<a

href="/contact"

data-analytics="challenge-cta"

class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white hover:bg-blue-700 transition"

>

Book a AI Discovery Session

</a>

</div>

</Container>

</section>